Package: tbit
Title: Version-Controlled Data Management for Reproducible Workflows
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Afshin", "Mashadi-Hossein", , "amashadihossein@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides version-controlled data management by abstracting tables 
    as code in git while storing actual data in cloud storage. Enables setting 
    up cloud-based repositories, syncing data with automatic versioning, 
    tracking complete data lineage, and accessing any historical version for 
    reproducibility. Designed for clinical and scientific workflows where 
    reproducibility is paramount.
